  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',false,'Korean','Mr. Sunshine','https://www.netflix.com/title/80991107','2020-09-27','day','2020-10-26','day','I watched this TV show based on a Netflix recommendation right after I finished watching the "The Lies Within" TV show. While I liked the acting and character development quite a bit, I was not a fan of the glorification of war and wanton killing in the TV show. My consumption of this TV show was slower than usual mostly because I was more preoccupied with work and other personal items during this month, so I often did not watch this show while preparing or eating meals.'),
  ('Netflix','Single video (such as movie)',false,'English','The Social Dilemma','https://www.netflix.com/title/81254224','2020-10-27','day','2020-10-30','day','I watched this movie based on a Netflix recommendation right after finishing the "Mr. Sunshine" TV show. Part of the reason for selecting this to watch was that I specifically wanted to pick a movie rather than a TV show so that I could finish it before my subscription expired. I think it made some good points, but largely overstated its case.'),
  ('Netflix','Single video (such as movie)',true,'English','The Trial of the Chicago 7','https://www.netflix.com/title/81043755','2020-10-31','day','2020-11-01','day','I watched this movie based on a past Netflix recommendation right after finishing the "The Social Dilemma" docudrama. Part of the reason for selecting this to watch was that I specifically wanted to pick a movie rather than a TV show so that I could finish it before my subscription expired. I thought the movie was well-done, though it did not go too deep into the backstory of the relevant incidents or political actors.'),
  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',true,'English','The Crown: Season 4','https://www.netflix.com/title/80025678','2020-12-20','day','2020-12-25','day','The season was released on 2020-11-15. I was taking a break from my Netflix subscription at the time; I started watching the season as soon as I resumed my Netflix subscription.'),
  ('Netflix','Single video (such as movie)',false,'English','Miss Americana','https://www.netflix.com/title/81028336','2020-12-25','day','2020-12-25','day','I watched this documentary film about Taylor Swift that I read about when Googling for stuff related to Taylor Swift a few days ago. I liked the documentary; I found particularly interesting her description of how she became politically active.'),
  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',true,'Korean','Start-Up','https://www.netflix.com/title/81290293','2020-12-29','day','2021-01-07','day','I watched this TV show based on both a Netflix recommendation and other positive reviews I had heard about it. I enjoyed it; it had the typical Park Hye-ryun feel from I Can Hear Your Voice, Pinoochio, and While You Were Sleeping.'),
  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',false,'Korean','Crash Landing on You','https://www.netflix.com/title/81159258','2021-01-07','day','2021-01-13','day','I watched this TV show based on repeated recommendation from Netflix as well as other positive reviews. I liked it quite a bit, including its in-depth portrayal of everyday life in North Korea.'),
  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',false,'English','The Queen''s Gambit','https://www.netflix.com/title/80234304','2021-01-14','day','2021-01-17','day','I watched this TV show based on both a Netflix recomendation and positive reviews, both published reviews and posts from my Facebook friends. After watching the series, I also watched https://www.netflix.com/title/81403290 (Creating the Queen''s Gambit).'),
  ('Netflix','Single video (such as movie)',true,'Hindi','Tribhanga - Tedhi Medhi Crazy','https://www.netflix.com/title/81205388','2021-01-17','day','2021-01-17','day','I watched this short movie (1 hour 35 minutes) on a whim based on it being featured on the Netflix home page. I was interested in watching only short pieces since I was pausing my Netflix subscription after two days. I liked the movie.'),
  ('Netflix','Single video (such as movie)',false,'English/Korean','BLACKPINK: Light Up the Sky','https://www.netflix.com/title/81106901','2021-01-18','day','2021-01-19','day','I watched this documentary about Korea-based girl group Blackpink that I had noticed through a previous Netflix recommendation a few weeks ago (likely recomended because I watched many Korean dramas on Netflix and had also watched Taylor Swift''s documentary). There was a mix of English and Korean used by the group members when explaining things; one of the members, who was Thai by origin, also spoke in Thai occasionally. I enjoyed watching this documentary. I had not previously heard of Blackpink. Part of my interest in selecting this was that I wanted to watch short pieces that I could finish before my Netflix subscription expired.'),
  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',false,'Korean','Vagabond','https://www.netflix.com/title/81095101','2021-03-22','day','2021-03-26','day','I watched this TV show based both on it showing up on the Netflix homepage and on it being listed in a list of good Korean dramas to watch on Netflix. I liked a lot of things about the show but had mixed feelings simmilar to those that https://www.dramabeans.com/2019/12/vagabond-episode-16-final/ describes.'),
