  ('Netflix','Single video (such as movie)',false,'Hindi','Is Love Enough? Sir','https://www.netflix.com/title/81136602','2021-04-04','day','2021-04-06','day','The movie was mainly in Hindi but also included some Marathi and some English. It was an interesting and sweet film.'),
  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',true,'English','The Big Day','https://www.netflix.com/title/81161576','2021-04-07','day','2021-04-09','day','This six-episode series (in two collecetions of three episodes each) covers two weddings per episode, going into various aspects of weddings and the love stories preceding them. Though interesting, it didn''t make me a fan of big, expensive weddings.'),
  ('Netflix','Series (such as TV show or web series)',false,'English','Indian Matchmaking','https://www.netflix.com/title/80244565','2021-04-09','day','2021-04-10','day','I watched this show after reading about it in a review of The Big Day, another Netflix show that I had just finished. It was an interesting window into a world I was not too familiar with.'),
