  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Optimize Your Body and Brain Right Now | Ben Greenfield on Conversations with Tom','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M9AV-wrgW9w','2021-01-04','day','2021-01-09','day','I heard about Ben Greenfield from a YouTube ad about his MindValley MasterClass. I was curious, so I looked for free videos by him and found this interview by Tom Bilyeu.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','5 Best Biohacks for Living Better & Longer | Ben Greenfield on Health Theory','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UneyRHeWPTg','2021-01-09','day','2021-01-10','day','I watched this interview of Ben Greenfield by Tom Bilyeu right after finishing another interview with the same interviewer and same interviewee. The suggestion was a YouTube recommendation.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Klan We Talk? | Daryl Davis | TEDxCapeMay','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fw0vS0qvYo0','2021-03-28','day','2021-03-28','day','I watched this video based on a link from https://fakenous.net/?p=2214 that I discovered from my Facebook feed. It was interesting.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Inside the mind of a master procrastinator | Tim Urban (TED talk)','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=arj7oStGLkU','2021-06-10','day','2021-06-10','day','I watched this video based on a YouTube recommendation on an unrelated video. I was familiar with Tim Urban through his work on the Wait But Why blog so the recommendation piqued my interest.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Moxie Wakes Up','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JcgwZk38FoY','2021-06-12','day','2021-06-12','day','I first came across Moxie via a YouTube ad. I shared Moxie with Issa, who sent me a link to this video in response. I found the video quite "cute" and it led me to wonder if cuteness will be part of AI''s takeover strategy.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Gilmore Girls Cast Reunion (Full Interview) | TODAY','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1j6bw5O6QKo','2021-07-19','day','2021-07-19','day','I watched this based on a YouTube recommendation. I had read elsewhere many of the nuggets talked about here, but a lot of the details were new to me. It was fun to listen to.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Gilmore Girls - Rory, the O.G. Annoying Millennial','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dKXTJvR1COw','2021-07-19','day','2021-07-19','day','I watched this based on a YouTube recommendation on the reunion video. I found it quite interesting albeit a bit harsh on Rory.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','AI & Logical Induction - Computerphile','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gDqkCxYYDGk','2021-08-12','day','2021-08-12','day','I watched this video from Robert Miles based on a link post https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/xHLEZPcM2myYauQW5/computerphile-discusses-miri-s-logical-induction-paper on LessWrong that I found while looking for information on https://intelligence.org/2016/09/12/new-paper-logical-induction/ (MIRI''s logical induction paper). I found it engaging and interesting; it may have been quicker to read the paper directly, but at the time I was in a particularly lazy mood so consuming a video felt easier.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','The Simplest Math Problem No One Can Solve','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=094y1Z2wpJg','2021-08-12','day','2021-08-12','day','I watched this video on the 3n + 1 conjecture (aka the Collatz conjecture) on seeing it as a recommendation after watching Robert Miles'' video explaining logical induction. This was mostly because I was feeling lazy and curious; I didn''t expect to gain significant value from the video. Nonetheless, the video was interesting and I learned a few new tidbits despite being generally familiar with the material already.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','WHY SUCCESS Comes From Mastering Negotiation In BUSINESS & LIFE | Chris Voss & Lewis Howes','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_iKeiPhisw','2021-09-15','day','2021-09-15','day','About an year ago I had watched another interview of Chris Voss by Lewis Howes, that I had liked. I realized that I had not watched this earlier interview, so I went ahead and watched (well, mostly listened to) it. Interestingly there was not a lot of overlap between the two videos, so my time spent listening was not wasted. I learned a lot of interesting tidbits by listening.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','"THIS IS WHY You Keep Having Relationship PROBLEMS!" | Dr. Shefali & Lewis Howes','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hBENly_svs0','2021-09-16','day','2021-09-16','day','After watching Lewis Howes'' interview with Chris Voss, I was looking for other interviews by Lewis Howes. I found this interview with Dr. Shefali and was somewhat interested, so I watched (or rather, mostly listened to) it. While I found it very interesting and it made many points that resonated with me, there were many parts that I did not agree with. One area: as with all people focused on a particular domain, I think the interviewee overestimated the importance of her domain in people''s lives.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','This Harvard Professor Explains the Secret to Aging in Reverse | David Sinclair on Health Theory','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IEz1P4i1P7s','2021-09-16','day','2021-09-16','day','I watched this video based on a YouTube recommendation and based on my general interest in life extension and senescence research. I''m loosely aware of several disagreement and controversies in this domain, so I did not watch this with the goal of believing at face value, but more to understand the space better. I had already previously watched other videos from the host Tom Bilyeu, specifically his interviews with Ben Greenfield.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','"This MINDSET SHIFT Will Let You Achieve ANYTHING YOU WANT In Life!" | Tom Bilyeu & Lewis Howes','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DN6BP65jWhk','2021-09-16','day','2021-09-16','day','Having watched interviews by both Tom Bilyeu and Lewis Howes, I was intrigued by the idea of one of them interviewing the other, so I ended up watching (or rather, mostly listening to) this interview of Tom Bilyeu by Lewis Howes. I felt this went more in-depth than other interviews by either of them, possibly because of a greater shared context between them leading to more curious questions. Overall, I found it quite intersting.')
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','Shyam Mohan bhaiya, Co founder of VMC tells the Study approach to follow in Half yearly exams','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l4U0Ovm4_Cc','2021-09-17','day','2021-09-17','day','I watched this video on a whim based on search results. I had attended this coaching institute when in high school and been taught physics by this person.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','How to deal with Stress - Must watch for School students, JEE and NEET aspirants and their parents','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESH7RszhL70','2021-09-17','day','2021-09-17','day','I had attended this coaching institute back when I was in high school, so I was interested to watch a video about it. It was interesting to listen to the material after several years of being away from the environment. One thought I had was how their advice was a mix of reasonable general life advice with a lot of stuff that made sense only in the very specific socio-cultural environment that their clientele were operating in. Although I had attended the coaching institute, my own interests had made me not quite part of their typical clientele, which is why although many of the things they said had resonated, many had not.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Everything You’ve Been Told About Money is WRONG | Ramit Sethi','https://impacttheory.com/episode/ramit-sethi-3/','2021-09-18','day','2021-09-18','day','I was looking through interviews by Tom Bilyeu and saw Ramit Sethi; I had previously heard of Ramit Sethi through https://www.kalzumeus.com/2012/01/23/salary-negotiation/ (by Patrick McKenzie). This mostly covered stuff around index investing to grow your money. I found it quite interesting even though I was broadly aware of the material discussed.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','This Is the Most Important Financial Advice You Need to Hear Right Now | Ramit Sethi','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mokyNBWZ8wg','2021-09-18','day','2021-09-18','day','I watched this video after watching another interview of Ramit Sethi by Tom Bilyeu. This video had been shot early in the COVID-19 pandemic, and was focused on how the COVID-19 pandemic affects financial advice.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','EVERYTHING You''ve Been Told About MONEY Is WRONG (How To Become Rich)| Ramit Sethi & Lewis Howes','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mZF8tDFX0gc','2021-09-18','day','2021-09-18','day','I watched this interview after watching two interviews of Ramit Sethi by Tom Bilyeu. It covered many similar themes but with a different emphasis: it first covered financial advice for wealthy/high-earning people (over $150,000 in annual income). It then covered financial advice for people earning less than $150,000/year.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','The Quick Part is a Lie, But This Guy Will Teach You How to Get Rich | Ramit Sethi on Impact Theory','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNK-9_Zp7wU','2021-09-18','day','2021-09-18','day','I watched this interview after watching two other interviews of Ramit Sethi by Tom Bilyeu and one interview by Lewis Howes. This focused more on salary negotiation. The advice seemed very similar to the negotiation advice offered by Christopher Voss in his negotiation MasterClass.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','The Zen Millionaire’s Secret to Creating Abundance | Ken Honda on Impact Theory','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PtifGrHy60g','2021-09-19','day','2021-09-19','day','I had heard about Ken Honda''s "arigato in arigato out" and was curious. After my curiosity in financial advice had been piqued by listening to various stuff of Ramit Sethi (including an interview by Tom Bilyeu), I decided to listen to this interview of Ken Honda by Tom Bilyeu.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','Magnetism 01','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wj40BOrFWng','2021-09-19','day','2021-09-19','day','When in high school, I had attended Vidyamandir Classes, a coaching institute. I was curious to see how I would evaluate their instruction style today. I saw this video and decided to watch it. I found the material engaging, but I was also struck by how narrowly tailored the focus was toward a specific form of learning and mastery that had been deemed most likely to help with examinations. NOTE: The talking is mostly in Hindi, with a little bit of English. The supporting written materials are in English.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','Magnetism 02','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7pkJKeIpnGI','2021-09-20','day','2021-09-20','day','I watched this after watching Magnetism 01, and had similar reactions. NOTE: The talking is mostly in Hindi, with a little bit of English. The supporting written materials are in English.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','Magnetism 03','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fsq0TsOftCo','2021-09-20','day','2021-09-20','day','I watched this after watching Magnetism 01 and Magnetism 02, and had similar reactions. NOTE: The talking is mostly in Hindi, with a little bit of English. The supporting written materials are in English.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','JEE Main 2020 - Last 30 days - How to prepare','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XXJEJy11YYs','2021-09-20','day','2021-09-20','day','When in high school, I had attended Vidyamandir Classes, a coaching institute. I was curious to see how I would think of their coaching philosophy after all these years I had also not attended the coaching all the way to the point equivalent to what this video covered, so it was interesting to hear how this would sound.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','Magnetism 04','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fry0jfdqSNQ','2021-09-20','day','2021-09-21','day','I watched this after watching Magnetism 01, Magnetism 02, and Magnetism 03, and had similar reactions. NOTE: The talking is mostly in Hindi, with a little bit of English. The supporting written materials are in English.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Lewis Howes REVEALS The One SKILL You Need to be SUCCESSFUL | Impact Theory','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hk-1lkVQiXc','2021-09-21','day','2021-09-21','day','I had previously watched the converse: an interview of Tom Bilyeu by Lewis Howes. That made me interested in how the interview in the other direction (Lewis Howes by Tom Bilyeu). It was interesting to see the kinds of topics covered with the tables flipped.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','The Biggest Myth In Education','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rhgwIhB58PA','2021-09-22','day','2021-09-22','day','I learned of this Veritasium video via a link from a friend. The video offers a critical take on learning styles and ends with a plug for using Google Search with more variation in search terms. It was reasonably enjoyable, though it agreed with my priors about learning styles so I didn''t have to update much.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Feynman Messenger Lectures - The Law of Gravitation - 1','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0LOnGjxP_pg','2021-09-22','day','2021-09-23','day','I had heard about the Feynman lectures for some time. I was prompted to listen to some of them while editing learning subwiki and noting some discussion of the Feynman technique in past edits by Issa Rice.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','JEE Main 2020 - Final message for D day by Bade bhaiya - Must watch for all JEE Main aspirants','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S0c1_XuYPbg','2021-09-24','day','2021-09-24','day','I had attendd Vidyamandir Classes while in high school. In the last week, I had been watching some videos put out by them. I decided to continue the tradition by watching one more video.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','Hindi','BADE BHAIYA Founder Vidyamandir Classes - Tips for JEE MAIN 2018','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tq01JzddKqA','2021-09-25','day','2021-09-25','day','I watched this video the day after watching https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S0c1_XuYPbg -- a similar video from the same person delivered two years later, in 2020.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Fireside Chat with Sam Bankman-Fried','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=--tV8U3BbJk','2021-11-08','day','2021-11-08','day','The video had been recommended to me a while back by a friend. I watched it finally in light of more recent news https://www.facebook.com/13934653/posts/10118866028010570/ related to Sam Bankman-Fried, the interviewee in the video. I found the interview quite interesting; it was interesting to see the shut-up-and-multiply utilitarianism as well as the raw ambition.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Duncan Sabien, Miranda Dixon-Luinenburg, Malo Bourgon, & Cathleen Kilgallen: Getting things done','https://forum.effectivealtruism.org/posts/QH5XFgRamDKeAt9cQ/duncan-sabien-miranda-dixon-luinenburg-malo-bourgon-and','2021-11-20','day','2021-11-20','day','I watched the video after running across it accidentally while searching for something else. I found the discussion of ops interesting though I didn''t have enough direct experience with ops to evaluate what the panelists said.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Can Bitcoin Become the World’s Money? A Soho Forum Debate','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ky7lB_tKVz0','2021-12-09','day','2021-12-09','day','I visited the Soho Forum past events page, looking for videos, and picked this video to watch. I found the topic and debate moderately interesting.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','I''m Leaving Medicine Forever (not clickbait)','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mZOVLrLXKCE','2021-12-19','day','2021-12-19','day','In this video, YouTube celebrity and junior doctor Ali Abdaal goes over his reasons for quitting medicine. The video discusses several ideas related to effective altruism and altruistic career choice. I found it to be an interesting dive into his decision-making process.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','Revealing My Investment Portfolio','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MgI6iquuuzA','2021-12-22','day','2021-12-22','day','I watched this video from Ali Abdaal based on a YouTube recommendation likely because I had previously watched another video of his. I found this video quite interesting, including his candid sharing of the exact finances breakdown, though I was already familiar with all his general themes.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','How Much Money I Earn as a Doctor + YouTuber','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VTTp5A-rSdc','2021-12-22','day','2021-12-22','day','In the video, Ali Abdaal explains how his income as a doctor compares with his income that directly or indirectly comes from his online stuff (YouTube, Skillshare, etc.) in 2020. He also describes how his online income grew from 2017 to 2020.'),
  ('YouTube','Single video (such as movie)','English','How I MAKE $27,000/ Week With PASSIVE INCOME & Productivity Secrets | Ali Abdaal & Lewis Howes','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UJoZMuxx0T8','2021-12-22','day','2021-12-22','day','This is an interview by Lewis Howes of Ali Abdaal. I watched this shortly after watching Ali Abdaal''s video about quitting medicine; excerpts from the interview video had been shown in the quitting medicine video; those excerpts covered areas where Lewis Howes challenged Ali Abdaal to think more seriously about the possibility of quitting medicine.');

